These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: mirinda, cola, tea, fanta
Pet: turtle, goldfish, bird, frog
1. Pet:frog is on the left of Beverage:tea##1
2. Beverage:mirinda is on the left of Pet:goldfish##1
3. Beverage:fanta is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:bird is on the left or right of Pet:frog##3
5. Beverage:mirinda is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | mirinda | cola | fanta | tea |
| Pet        | turtle | goldfish   | frog | bird    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: adventure, romance, satire, sports
Nationality: australian, british, indonesian, thai
1. Movie-Genre:romance is on the left of Movie-Genre:sports##1
2. Nationality:australian is on the left of Nationality:indonesian##1
3. Nationality:indonesian is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:australian == Movie-Genre:adventure##1
5. Nationality:british is on the right of Nationality:indonesian##1
6. Nationality:australian == Movie-Genre:adventure##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | adventure  | romance  | sports |
| Nationality   | thai    | australian | indonesian | british    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: kale, corn, grapefruit, garlic
Movie-Genre: satire, epic, scientific, family
1. Food:garlic is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:family##3
2. Food:grapefruit is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:family is on the left or right of Food:corn##3
4. Movie-Genre:family is on the right of Movie-Genre:scientific##1
5. Movie-Genre:satire is in an odd position##4
6. Food:corn is on the right of Food:grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | garlic | grapefruit | corn    | kale      |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific        | family     | satire | epic |

