.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: singing, collecting, rock-climbing, hiking
Music-Genre: techno, punk, hip-hop, r&b
1. Hobby:collecting is between Music-Genre:techno and Music-Genre:r&b##2
2. Hobby:hiking is on the left of Hobby:singing##1
3. Music-Genre:hip-hop is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:punk is on the left of Music-Genre:r&b##1
5. Music-Genre:punk is on the right of Hobby:singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | hiking | singing | collecting | rock-climbing |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop       | techno   | punk    | r&b  |

