.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Music-Genre: rock, disco, salsa, indie
Nationality: turkish, japanese, canadian, nigerian
1. Music-Genre:salsa is on the right of Nationality:nigerian##1
2. Nationality:japanese == Music-Genre:indie##1
3. Nationality:canadian is on the right of Music-Genre:rock##1
4. Music-Genre:disco is on the far left##1
5. Music-Genre:salsa is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:turkish is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | disco  | rock    | salsa   | indie       |
| Nationality   | turkish | nigerian | canadian | japanese |

