4. Job:firefighter is on the right of Pet:rat##1
5. Job:engineer is between Job:firefighter and Job:journalist##2
6. Pet:pony is in an odd position##4
7. Pet:pony is between Job:engineer and Pet:dog##2
8. Job:engineer is on the left or right of Job:journalist##3

