.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
Beverage: milk, hot-chocolate, tea, coffee
Music-Genre: reggae, trance, pop, house
1. Beverage:milk == Music-Genre:house##1
2. Music-Genre:reggae is on the right of Beverage:milk##1
3. Music-Genre:house is between Music-Genre:reggae and Beverage:tea##2
4. Beverage:milk is in an odd position##4
5. Music-Genre:house is on the left or right of Music-Genre:reggae##3
6. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left or right of Music-Genre:trance##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate       | tea   | milk | coffee |
| Music-Genre   | pop | trance | house        | reggae    |

