.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
Beverage: lemonade, sprite, cola, mirinda
Food: papaya, garlic, cucumber, cranberry
1. Food:garlic is on the far left##1
2. Beverage:cola is on the left or right of Beverage:lemonade##3
3. Beverage:mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:cucumber is on the left of Food:cranberry##1
5. Food:cranberry is on the right of Beverage:lemonade##1
6. Food:cucumber is in an even position##4
7. Food:papaya == Beverage:sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | mirinda | lemonade    | cola       | sprite |
| Food       | garlic  | cucumber | cranberry | papaya  |

